3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Hobby         | writing   | rock-climbing |
| Flower           | bellflower | zinnia    |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | indie         |
| Sport         | sailing   | weightlifting |

