2 different pets are kept: frog, goat
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the doctor is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
3. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Music-Genre    | punk | gospel    |
| Job         | doctor        | designer |
| Pet         | frog          | goat     |
| Transport   | roller        | tram     |

 